<section class="bg-white section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brand-red mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is mobile pizza catering?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Mobile pizza catering brings our wood-fired pizza oven directly to your event location. We set up on-site and prepare fresh, authentic Neapolitan-style pizzas made to order for you and your guests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How does Bello Pizza work?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We arrive at your location with our mobile pizza oven, set up our station, and begin preparing fresh pizzas throughout your event. Our team handles all the cooking and service, allowing you to enjoy your event worry-free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Is the Bello Pizza menu customizable?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Yes! We offer customizable menu options including various pizza styles, toppings, salads, meatballs, pasta, and wings. We can accommodate dietary restrictions and preferences to ensure all your guests are satisfied.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is the typical catering experience timeline?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We arrive 1-2 hours before your event to set up and preheat our wood-fired oven. Service typically lasts 2-4 hours depending on your package. We handle all cleanup and breakdown after your event concludes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What area do you serve?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We serve all of Southern California, from Los Angeles to San Diego. Travel fees may apply for events outside our 25-mile radius. Contact us for specific location availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How far in advance should I book?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We recommend booking at least 2-3 weeks in advance, especially for weekend events. During peak season (spring and summer), we suggest booking 4-6 weeks ahead to ensure availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Do you accommodate dietary restrictions?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Absolutely! We offer gluten-free dough options, vegan cheese, and can prepare pizzas without specific allergens. Please inform us of any dietary needs when booking so we can accommodate your guests properly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What equipment do you need from the venue?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We are completely self-contained! We bring our own mobile oven, prep stations, serving equipment, and staff. We only need access to electricity and a flat surface for setup. No kitchen facilities required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const questions = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question');
    
    questions.forEach(question => {
      question.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const item = this.closest('.faq-item');
        const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
        const icon = this.querySelector('.faq-icon');
        
        // Close other open items
        questions.forEach(otherQuestion => {
          if (otherQuestion !== question) {
            const otherItem = otherQuestion.closest('.faq-item');
            const otherAnswer = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-answer');
            const otherIcon = otherQuestion.querySelector('.faq-icon');
            otherAnswer.classList.add('hidden');
            otherIcon.textContent = '+';
            otherIcon.classList.remove('rotate-45');
          }
        });
        
        // Toggle current item
        answer.classList.toggle('hidden');
        if (answer.classList.contains('hidden')) {
          icon.textContent = '+';
          icon.classList.remove('rotate-45');
        } else {
          icon.textContent = 'Ã—';
          icon.classList.add('rotate-45');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>